<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-05-23T12:24:20+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Sat, 23 May 2026 12:24:20 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[Over 80 killed in gas explosion at coal mine in China’s Shanxi province]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131272434.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A devastating gas explosion at the Liushenyu coal mine in northern China's Shanxi province has claimed the lives of at least 82 miners. The blast occurred Friday evening, with carbon monoxide levels reportedly exceeding limits prior to the incident. Rescue operations are ongoing as President Xi Jinping has ordered a full-scale rescue and a thorough investigation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-coal-mine-blast-several-killed-after-gas-explosion-in-shanxi-rescue-operations-for-trapped-under-way/articleshow/131272434.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-coal-mine-blast-several-killed-after-gas-explosion-in-shanxi-rescue-operations-for-trapped-under-way/articleshow/131272434.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T10:47:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131272663,imgsize-1326564.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Poor thing': Iran mocks Donald Trump as viral buffalo resembling him loses appetite]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131271775.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran's official account in Russia shared a viral video of a Bangladeshi albino buffalo resembling Donald Trump, claiming the animal lost its appetite due to the comparison amid ongoing US-Iran conflict. The buffalo, named 'Donald Trump', has become a local attraction ahead of Eid al-Adha festivities.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/poor-thing-iran-mocks-donald-trump-as-viral-buffalo-resembling-him-loses-appetite/articleshow/131271775.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/poor-thing-iran-mocks-donald-trump-as-viral-buffalo-resembling-him-loses-appetite/articleshow/131271775.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T10:13:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131272164,imgsize-857857.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Revenge matter of time': IRGC-trained Iraqi arrested over assassination plot against Donald Trump's daughter Ivanka]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131271352.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[An IRGC-trained operative, allegedly seeking revenge for Qasem Soleimani's death, was arrested in Turkey and extradited to the US. Mohammad Baqer Saad Dawood Al-Saadi is accused of plotting to assassinate Ivanka Trump, even possessing a blueprint of her Florida home. He reportedly made threats against Americans online.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/revenge-matter-of-time-irgc-trained-iraqi-arrested-over-assassination-plot-against-donald-trumps-daughter-ivanka/articleshow/131271352.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/revenge-matter-of-time-irgc-trained-iraqi-arrested-over-assassination-plot-against-donald-trumps-daughter-ivanka/articleshow/131271352.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T08:49:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131271486,imgsize-858080.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: SpaceX Starship bursts into flames during fiery Indian Ocean splashdown after test flight]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131270952.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[SpaceX's Starship rocket completed its 12th test flight with a controlled splashdown in the Indian Ocean, despite engine malfunctions and a booster issue. The massive spacecraft deployed mock satellites during its high-risk mission. This crucial test flight advances SpaceX's lunar ambitions for NASA's Artemis program and comes amid reports of a potential IPO.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/watch-spacex-starship-bursts-into-flames-during-fiery-indian-ocean-splashdown-after-test-flight/articleshow/131270952.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/watch-spacex-starship-bursts-into-flames-during-fiery-indian-ocean-splashdown-after-test-flight/articleshow/131270952.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T07:47:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131271036,imgsize-4958070.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[YouTuber Danny Go’s son Isaac Coleman’s cause of death: Inside the 14-year-old’s battle with rare illness]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131270509.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[YouTuber Danny Go, whose real name is Daniel Coleman, announced the death of his 14-year-old son Isaac Coleman on May 21, 2026. Isaac had Fanconi anemia, a rare genetic disorder, and was later diagnosed with mouth cancer in 2025. In an emotional tribute, Danny praised his son’s strength, joy, and resilience through years of health struggles. Fans and fellow creators flooded social media with condolences and support for the grieving family.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/youtuber-danny-gos-son-isaac-colemans-cause-of-death-inside-the-14-year-olds-battle-with-rare-illness/articleshow/131270509.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/youtuber-danny-gos-son-isaac-colemans-cause-of-death-inside-the-14-year-olds-battle-with-rare-illness/articleshow/131270509.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T05:38:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131270509,imgsize-37602.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[ChudTheBuilder may be released after reported $1M bond offer from crypto casino “Duel”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131268163.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A significant development in the ChudTheBuilder case sees a crypto gambling platform, Duel, reportedly offering to pay his $1 million bond. This unexpected financial backing for the individual facing serious charges linked to a courthouse shooting has ignited widespread online discussion. The court is yet to confirm the bond's acceptance, leaving many to speculate on the platform's motives.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/chudthebuilder-may-be-released-after-reported-1m-bond-offer-from-crypto-casino-duel/articleshow/131268163.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/chudthebuilder-may-be-released-after-reported-1m-bond-offer-from-crypto-casino-duel/articleshow/131268163.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T02:47:08+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131268162,imgsize-682779.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[YouTube star Danny Go mourns heartbreaking loss of 14-year-old son Isaac]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131268121.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[YouTube sensation Danny Go, known as Daniel Coleman, shared the heartbreaking news of his 14-year-old son Isaac's passing after a battle with cancer. Coleman expressed profound grief, celebrating Isaac's strength and joy despite his health challenges. The family, including wife Mindy, focused on creating cherished memories during Isaac's final months, leaving fans worldwide deeply saddened.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/youtube-star-danny-go-mourns-heartbreaking-loss-of-14-year-old-son-isaac/articleshow/131268121.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/youtube-star-danny-go-mourns-heartbreaking-loss-of-14-year-old-son-isaac/articleshow/131268121.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T02:01:36+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131268116,imgsize-806318.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Go home' for Green Card rule: Immigration attorney Rahul Reddy explains what H-1B visa holders should do now]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131267879.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/go-home-for-green-card-rule-immigration-attorney-rahul-reddy-explains-what-h-1b-visa-holders-should-do-now/articleshow/131267879.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/go-home-for-green-card-rule-immigration-attorney-rahul-reddy-explains-what-h-1b-visa-holders-should-do-now/articleshow/131267879.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T01:21:45+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131267897,imgsize-45738.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Shocking reality of 100 families living beneath Manila highways in the Philippines]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131264951.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/shocking-reality-of-100-families-living-beneath-manila-highways-in-the-philippines/articleshow/131264951.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/shocking-reality-of-100-families-living-beneath-manila-highways-in-the-philippines/articleshow/131264951.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T20:12:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/eleme