/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131265025,imgsize-229560.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Did China spy on Musk, tech executives during Trump's Beijing visit? Blogger makes big claim]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131264314.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/did-china-spy-on-elon-musk-other-tech-executives-during-trumps-beijing-visit-blogger-makes-big-claim/articleshow/131264314.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/did-china-spy-on-elon-musk-other-tech-executives-during-trumps-beijing-visit-blogger-makes-big-claim/articleshow/131264314.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T19:13:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131264642,imgsize-19914.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Nobel Prize winner Olga Tokarczuk under fire after revealing she uses AI to develop ideas]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131264613.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nobel-prize-winner-olga-tokarczuk-under-fire-after-revealing-she-uses-ai-to-develop-ideas/articleshow/131264613.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nobel-prize-winner-olga-tokarczuk-under-fire-after-revealing-she-uses-ai-to-develop-ideas/articleshow/131264613.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T19:19:28+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131264697,imgsize-637431.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Pakistan gets its own ‘Cockroach Awaam Party’ as India’s viral CJP sparks cross-border satire wave]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131263286.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Inspired by India's viral Cockroach Janta Party, satirical groups like the Cockroach Awami Party and Cockroach Awami League have emerged in Pakistan. These social media-driven parties, adopting similar themes, aim to represent "lazy and unemployed" youth and Gen-Z, offering an alternative to established political factions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-gets-its-own-cockroach-awaam-party-as-indias-viral-cjp-sparks-cross-border-satire-wave/articleshow/131263286.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-gets-its-own-cockroach-awaam-party-as-indias-viral-cjp-sparks-cross-border-satire-wave/articleshow/131263286.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T17:37:54+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131263333,imgsize-1128827.cms"/></item></channel></rss>